column4: Tesla Signature series Model X to begin delivery September 29
column5: SAN FRANCISCO Tesla Motors Inc  said on Wednesday it would begin delivering its first luxury electric crossovers  the Model X Signature series  on Sept. 29 to customers who have already reserved the sport utility vehicles.

column4: UPDATE 1-Tesla Signature series Model X to begin delivery Sept 29
column5: SAN FRANCISCO  Sept 2 Tesla Motors Inc  said on Wednesday it would begin delivering its first luxury electric crossovers  the Model X Signature series  on Sept. 29 to customers who have already reserved the sport utility vehicles.

column4: Tesla Signature series Model X priced at $132 000 to $144 000
column5: SAN FRANCISCO  Sept 2 Tesla Motors Inc  said on Wednesday that customers who reserved its first luxury electric crossover  the Model X Signature series  could now customize their models  with prices ranging from $132 000 and $144 000.
